race.comment: WINSOME RAMBO (2) could manage only second but ran fast time (29.67) at this track over 520m. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. TANK KEEPING (1) was a last start winner (29.61) from Box 8 at this track. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Expected to measure up again. OUR MUMMA JO (3) is progressing well scoring last time out (29.66) at this track and bringing up her 10th career win. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Has put together a string of wins and expected to go close again.
